Package ohos.ai.nlu

Interface OnResultListener<T>


  • public interface OnResultListener<T>
    Provides a callback for observing NLU method calls.

    The caller determines how to implement this interface when using NluClient#init(Context, OnResultListener, boolean) to initialize the NLU engine.

    Since:
    3

    • Method Detail

      • onResult

        void onResult​(T result)
        Called after the NLU engine is initialized or NLU text is parsed.

        After the NLU engine is initialized by using NluClient#init(Context, OnResultListener, boolean), the NLU enginer server invokes this callback to process the initialization result data and parsed text. The caller determines how to implement this callback.

        Parameters:
        result - Indicates the NLU initialization result data.
        Since:
        3
